      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document specifies a method for exchanging IPv6 traffic engineering information using the IS-IS routing protocol.  This information enables routers in an IS-IS network to calculate traffic-engineered routes using IPv6 addresses. [STANDARDS-TRACK]&lt;/p&gt;</t>
